Yes ☺️ I'M CANCER FREE NOW 😄❤️

Waking up being CANCER FREE is a wonderful feeling that you can ever imagine.. (I had Follicular Lymphoma)

Since 2.5 years, I always wondered what this would actually feel like?  How would I react to it?  What would I do the moment I know?

And to be honest, the first thing that happened was THANK YOU @jeetmakwana09 & GOD🙏🏻💫 for being with me in this process every moment no matter how bad the situation was ❤️

Honestly I believed in the process, CANCER was just a part of my life now. I have got so many dms, texts, calls and emails from all the wonderful people (that includes EACH ONE OF YOU who even thought about me.)

The only thing I did in this entire process of healing, was to be POSITIVE and BELIEVE in me. I have learned so much about being spiritual, faithful, holistic, well-being, well-balanced, immune system, mindset, and EVERYTHING that  made actual sense in my life!

I'll definitely set some time and share everything with you all everything in my stories!

BUT for now YOUR GIRL IS CANCER FREE!! Trust Mr even typing and the thought of sharing this to everyone is making me smile with tears in my eyes.

THANK YOU EACH & EVERYONE!! THANK YOU GOD!
